The paper focuses on the precise calculation of similarity factors between papers and reviewers for automatic assignment of reviewers to papers. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and deep learning (cs.DL). The use of taxonomy of keywords to describe competences is also relevant to these sub-categories.
